{"id":5096,"date":"2021-04-27T10:58:30","date_gmt":"2021-04-27T03:58:30","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/?p=5096"},"modified":"2023-05-11T11:25:23","modified_gmt":"2023-05-11T04:25:23","slug":"mothers-day-vi","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/mothers-day-vi\/","title":{"rendered":"Ng\u00e0y c\u1ee7a M\u1eb9 t\u1ea1i Reflections"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-4gfk9986 fg-image  img-responsive full-width fg-text-dark\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mothers-Day-Dinner.jpg 1992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/225d494016cccb6346bdfc14e79919e3_Mothers-Day-Dinner-320-c-100.jpg 320w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/225d494016cccb6346bdfc14e79919e3_Mothers-Day-Dinner-768-c-100.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/225d494016cccb6346bdfc14e79919e3_Mothers-Day-Dinner-992-c-100.jpg 992w, https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/225d494016cccb6346bdfc14e79919e3_Mothers-Day-Dinner-1200-c-100.jpg 1200w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1992px) 100vw, 1992px\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/Mothers-Day-Dinner.jpg\" alt=\"Mothers-Day-Dinner\"><style><\/style><script type=\"text\/javascript\"><\/script><section class=\"ffb-id-4sbfvkl1 fg-section fg-text-dark\" id=\"intro\"><div class=\"fg-container container fg-container-large fg-container-lvl--1 \"><div class=\"fg-row row    \" ><img decoding=\"async\" class=\"ffb-id-4sbfvkl2 fg-image  img-responsive fg-text-dark\" src=\"https:\/\/www.caravellehotel.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/freshizer\/b598c739837858f264fe42f99107a46f_Logo-Reflections-Restaurant-300-c-90.png\" alt=\"Logo-Reflections-Restaurant\"><div class=\"ffb-id-4sbfvkl3 fg-col col-xs-12 col-md-12 fg-text-dark\"><h1 class=\"ffb-id-4sbfvkl7 fg-heading text-center    fg-text-dark\">NG\u00c0Y C\u1ee6A M\u1eb8<\/h1><div class=\"ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 fg-paragraph ff-richtext text-left    fg-text-dark\"><\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng k\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m Ng&agrave;y c\u1ee7a M\u1eb9 trong kh&ocirc;ng gian tuy\u1ec7t di\u1ec7u t\u1ea1i nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng Reflections!<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">H&atilde;y c&ugrave;ng ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i th\u01b0\u1edfng th\u1ee9c \u0111&ecirc;m ti\u1ec7c su\u1ed1t cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n v&agrave; v&agrave;o Ng&agrave;y c\u1ee7a M\u1eb9 t\u1ea1i Trung t&acirc;m S&agrave;i G&ograve;n v\u1edbi th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n \u0111\u1ea7y tinh t\u1ebf c\u1ee7a B\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edfng Ivan Barone; ti\u1ec7c t\u1ed1i 5 m&oacute;n h\u1ea5p d\u1eabn v&agrave; th\u1ef1c \u0111\u01a1n g\u1ecdi m&oacute;n \u0111\u1ee7 lo\u1ea1i s\u1ebd l&agrave;m th\u1ecfa m&atilde;n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi s&agrave;nh \u0103n.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ec3 b\u1eefa ti\u1ec7c t\u1ed1i th&ecirc;m ph\u1ea7n \u0111&aacute;ng nh\u1edb, Sommelier c\u1ee7a ch&uacute;ng t&ocirc;i \u0111&atilde; chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb c&aacute;c lo\u1ea1i r\u01b0\u1ee3u ngon nh\u1ea5t, r\u01b0\u1ee3u vang, r\u01b0\u1ee3u champagne \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t nh\u1ea5t \u0111\u1ec3 Qu&yacute; kh&aacute;ch c&oacute; m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1ed1i ho&agrave;n h\u1ea3o trong b\u1ea7u kh&ocirc;ng kh&iacute; tinh t\u1ebf v&agrave; trang nh&atilde; nh\u1ea5t.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110&ecirc;m ti\u1ec7c K\u1ef7 ni\u1ec7m Ng&agrave;y c\u1ee7a M\u1eb9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Th\u1ee9 S&aacute;u, 07 th&aacute;ng 5 \u0111\u1ebfn Ch\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt, 09 th&aacute;ng 5 n\u0103m 2021 v\u1edbi gi&aacute; VN\u0110 1,350,000++ m\u1ed9t kh&aacute;ch.<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center\">&Aacute;p d\u1ee5ng c&aacute;c quy\u1ec1n l\u1ee3i theo ti&ecirc;u chu\u1ea9n d&agrave;nh ri&ecirc;ng cho c&aacute;c th&agrave;nh vi&ecirc;n C&acirc;u l\u1ea1c b\u1ed9 Caravelle Classic Club.<\/p>\n<p><\/div><div class=\"ffb-id-4sbg15uo buttons-el-wrapper text-center    fg-text-dark\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.tablecheck.com\/en\/shops\/reflections-restaurant\/reserve\" class=\"ffb-block-button-1-0 ffb-btn ffb-btn-v1 ffb-btn-link  btn-base-brd-slide btn-slide  btn-base-xs    btn-w-auto fg-text-dark ffb-button1-1\" title=\"TableCheck - Reflections Restaurant\"><span class=\"btn-text\">\u0110\u1eb6T B\u00c0N<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/div><\/section><style>.ffb-id-4sbfvkl1{ padding-top: 50px;padding-right: 50px;padding-bottom: 50px;padding-left: 50px;} .ffb-id-4sbfvkl1{ text-align: center;} .ffb-id-4sbfvkl3{ text-align: center;}.ffb-id-4sbg15uo .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ color:#ffffff;}.ffb-id-4sbg15uo .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ color:#ffffff;}.ffb-id-4sbg15uo .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ border-color: transparent;}.ffb-id-4sbg15uo .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ border-color: transparent;}.ffb-id-4sbg15uo .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide{ background-color:#490042;}.ffb-id-4sbg15uo .ffb-button1-1.ffb-block-button-1-0.btn-base-brd-slide:hover{ background-color:#490042;}.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 ,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:before,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:after,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *:before,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *:after{ color: #797979 !important;}.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:before,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:after,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:hover,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:focus,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *:before,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *:after,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *:hover,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 *:focus{ font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif, Arial, sans-serif !important;}.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3{ font-size: 13px !important;}.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3 ,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:before,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3:after,.ffb-id-4sbg0pd3